## âš™ï¸ Configuration

All configuration is in `config.py`:

```python
class Config:
    # LLM Models
    DEEP_THINKING_MODEL = "gpt-4o"      # For complex reasoning
    QUICK_THINKING_MODEL = "gpt-4o-mini" # For fast operations

    # Debate Settings
    MAX_DEBATE_ROUNDS = 2
    MAX_RISK_DISCUSS_ROUNDS = 1

    # Memory Settings
    MAX_MEMORIES = 100
    SIMILARITY_THRESHOLD = 0.7

    # ... and more
```

